      "raw_text": "Columbia river valley the scene of\ngreat activity. One of the interest\ning questions connected with the\ngreat Improvement OF the Columbia\nRiver valley is where the market\nwill be. There are several rumors\nafioat. One Is to the effect that the\nColumbia and Okanogan steamer tine\nwill carry the products of the valley\nby boat down the river and by way\nof Wenatchee to Seattle. thereby cut\nting Spokane entirely out. On the\nother hand. there are several rumors\nto the effect that the irrigation COM\npany will place. boat of It's own\non the river and connect at the\nmouth of the Spokane river with an\nelectric line TO be built from Spokane\nto that point."
